!! Version 0.0.14

!!! New Features

* ''Language Switcher'' - Temporarily switch editor language mode without changing tiddler type
** Toolbar dropdown button with all installed languages
** Keyboard shortcut `Ctrl+Alt+L` opens picker panel within editor
** Supports TiddlyWiki, Markdown, HTML, CSS, JavaScript, TypeScript, JSON, YAML, XML, Python, Plain Text
** Configurable persistence: session-only or save to `codemirror-type` field
** Config tiddler: `$:/config/codemirror-6/languageSwitcherPersist`

* ''CodeMirror Keyboard Shortcuts'' - Support for editor-specific keyboard shortcuts
** New tag `$:/tags/KeyboardShortcut/CodeMirror` for registering shortcuts
** Shortcuts can use `((shortcut-name))` reference syntax
** `handleKeydownEvent` method checks and executes registered shortcuts

