!! Version 0.0.13

!!! Improvements

* ''Consistent Selection Highlighting'' - Selected text now has uniform appearance
** Selection background and text color applied consistently regardless of formatting
** Bold, italic, and other styled text no longer bleeds through selection
** Works for both primary and secondary (multi-cursor) selections

* ''Cursor Styling'' - Improved cursor visibility
** Cursor now extends slightly above and below the text line
** Default blink rate changed to 530ms (matches Windows/VS Code standard)

* ''Lucide Icons'' - Updated toolbar icons to use Lucide icon set
** Undo: `undo-2`
** Redo: `redo-2`
** Show Trailing Whitespace: `pilcrow`
** Remove Trailing Whitespace: `eraser`
** Spellcheck: `spell-check-2`

* ''License Files'' - Added MIT license to all plugins
** Main editor plugin includes Lucide Icons ISC license attribution

---

!! Version 0.0.12

!!! New Plugins

* ''Image Preview Plugin'' - Inline preview of images in the editor
** Shows image previews after `[img[source]]` syntax
** Supports both tiddler images and external URLs
** Shows "[Image not found]" for missing tiddlers
** Config tiddler: `$:/config/codemirror-6/imagePreview`

* ''Color Picker Plugin'' - Inline color swatches with click-to-edit
** Displays color swatches next to hex colors (`#fff`, `#ff0000`)
** Supports `rgb()`, `rgba()`, `hsl()`, and `hsla()` colors
** Click swatch to open native color picker and update the color
** Config tiddler: `$:/config/codemirror-6/colorPicker`

* ''Word Count Plugin'' - Live word, character, and line count display
** Shows counts in a panel below the editor
** Updates on document changes and selection changes
** When text is selected, shows "selected / total" counts
** Config tiddler: `$:/config/codemirror-6/wordCount`

!!! New Features

* ''Complete Any Word'' - Configurable fallback word completion from document
** Suggests words that appear elsewhere in the document when no other completions match
** Toggle on/off in ControlPanel (disabled by default)
** Config tiddler: `$:/config/codemirror-6/completeAnyWord`

!!! Improvements

* ''Multi-Cursor Toolbar Operations'' - Toolbar buttons now work with multiple selections
** Bold, italic, and other wrap-style operations apply to all cursors independently
** Proper toggle behavior: each selection checks for existing markers and adds/removes accordingly
** Fixes `tm-edit-text-operation` messages to pass prefix/suffix for multi-cursor support

* ''Extended Close Brackets'' - Additional quote pairs for auto-closing
** Curly/typographic quotes: `""` and `''`
** German-style quotes: `„"` and `‚'`
** All pairs work with the close brackets feature when enabled

* ''Auto Close Tags Filter Context'' - No longer triggers inside filter expressions
** Uses syntax tree to detect `FilterExpression`, `FilterRun`, `FilteredTransclusion` contexts
** Prevents `<variable>` in filters like `[<myvar>]` from getting a closing tag

