!! Version 0.0.11

!!! New Features

* ''Undo/Redo Toolbar Buttons'' - Dedicated toolbar buttons for undo and redo
** Custom `tm-cm6-undo` and `tm-cm6-redo` messages for direct CodeMirror integration
** New icons for undo and redo actions

* ''Trailing Whitespace Highlighting'' - Toggle to show trailing whitespace
** New toolbar button to toggle visibility on/off
** Config tiddler `$:/config/codemirror-6/showTrailingWhitespace`
** Uses CodeMirror compartments for live toggling

* ''Remove Trailing Whitespace'' - Toolbar button to clean up trailing whitespace
** Removes trailing whitespace from all lines in a single operation
** Single undo step for the entire cleanup

* ''Multi-line Macro Calls'' - Parser now supports macros spanning multiple lines
** Macros like `<<tabs\n  param:"value"\n>>` are now properly parsed
** Parameters on separate lines are correctly highlighted

!!! Lint Plugin Improvements

* ''Orphan Closing Tag Detection'' - Detects closing tags without matching opening tags
** Reports `</div>` or `</$widget>` that have no corresponding opening tag
** "Remove closing tag" quick-fix action
** Works for both HTML tags and widgets

* ''Fixed HTMLBlock False Positives'' - Self-contained HTML blocks no longer reported as unclosed
** `<div>content</div>` on multiple lines correctly recognized as closed

!!! Bug Fixes

* ''Unclosed Code Block Parsing'' - Fixed last character being styled incorrectly
** Documents without trailing newlines now handled correctly
** Uses `prevLineEnd()` instead of `lineStart - 1` for proper end position

